#. Translators: Message about block recovery after plugin updates.
#: inc/admin-notice.php:66
msgid ""
"PDFjs Viewer has been updated.\n"
"\n"
"If you edit a post that contains a PDF, you may see a message with an \"Attempt Block Recovery\" button. Simply click it as this is a normal part of how WordPress handles updates.\n"
"\n"
"If you choose not to recover the block, your existing PDFs will still work perfectly, and your visitors won't see any changes."
msgstr ""

